      <title>越南的咖啡输出在干旱上下降，增加了紧缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/vietnam-s-coffee-output-dips-on-drought-adding-to-global-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于天气恶劣，越南本赛季的咖啡产量预计将低于上一年，这使全球价格上涨的供应短缺加剧了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/vietnam-s-coffee-output-dips-on-drought-adding-to-global-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 02:42:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
